props.value: dtalk|0|dtalk|1|Name's Darell. You new here? ... Have any tiles?
dtalk|1|dtalk|2|Huh? Why are you out here and not with your tiles??
dtalk|2|dtalk|3|Dang, some people are so careless...
dtalk|3|dtalk|4|In this world, you gotta protect what's yours.
dtalk|4|dtalk|5|Take two steps away from a claimed tile and BAM! Stolen!
dtalk|5|dtalk|6|My bud Jeremy offered me this tile a year ago.
dtalk|6|dtalk|7|He's a swell guy, he really is.
dtalk|7|dtalk|8|I've been grooving out on this tile since I claimed it~
dtalk|8|dtalk|9|And hey, the location's not too bad!
dtalk|9|dtalk|10|Nice view of the sea~ And plenty of people pass through too~
dtalk|10|dtalk|11|Just gotta be careful when the tide rises heh...
dtalk|11|dtalk|12|Since you're out here I'll assume you're -tileless-.
dtalk|12|dtalk|13|In case you didn't know... Not all tiles are claimable.
dtalk|13|dtalk|14|And not all claimable tiles can be claimed the same way.
dtalk|14|dtalk|15|Go out and try to claim some tiles.
dtalk|15|dtalk|16|You might have to get clever to claim some heh...
dtalk|16|Once you claim a tile, it'll have a golden sheen~
